branches_dump:
SELECT branches.branch, branches.parent, branches.parent_turn, branches.parent_tick, branches.end_turn, branches.end_tick 
FROM branches ORDER BY branches.branch
branches_insert: INSERT INTO branches (branch, parent, parent_turn, parent_tick, end_turn, end_tick) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
create_branches:
CREATE TABLE branches (
	branch TEXT NOT NULL, 
	parent TEXT, 
	parent_turn INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	parent_tick INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	end_turn INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	end_tick INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	PRIMARY KEY (branch), 
	CHECK (branch<>parent), 
	FOREIGN KEY(branch) REFERENCES branches (parent)
)
create_edge_val:
CREATE TABLE edge_val (
	graph TEXT NOT NULL, 
	orig TEXT NOT NULL, 
	dest TEXT NOT NULL, 
	idx INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	"key" TEXT NOT NULL, 
	branch TEXT NOT NULL, 
	turn INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	tick INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	prev TEXT, 
	value TEXT, 
	PRIMARY KEY (graph, orig, dest, idx, "key", branch, turn, tick), 
	FOREIGN KEY(graph, orig, dest, idx) REFERENCES edges (graph, orig, dest, idx), 
	FOREIGN KEY(branch) REFERENCES branches (branch)
)
create_edges:
CREATE TABLE edges (
	graph TEXT NOT NULL, 
	orig TEXT NOT NULL, 
	dest TEXT NOT NULL, 
	idx INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	branch TEXT NOT NULL, 
	turn INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	tick INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	extant BOOLEAN NOT NULL, 
	PRIMARY KEY (graph, orig, dest, idx, branch, turn, tick), 
	FOREIGN KEY(graph, orig) REFERENCES nodes (graph, node), 
	FOREIGN KEY(graph, dest) REFERENCES nodes (graph, node), 
	FOREIGN KEY(graph) REFERENCES graphs (graph), 
	FOREIGN KEY(branch) REFERENCES branches (branch), 
	CHECK (extant IN (0, 1))
)
create_global:
CREATE TABLE global (
	"key" TEXT NOT NULL, 
	value TEXT, 
	PRIMARY KEY ("key")
)
create_graph_val:
CREATE TABLE graph_val (
	graph TEXT NOT NULL, 
	"key" TEXT NOT NULL, 
	branch TEXT NOT NULL, 
	turn INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	tick INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	prev TEXT, 
	value TEXT, 
	PRIMARY KEY (graph, "key", branch, turn, tick), 
	FOREIGN KEY(graph) REFERENCES graphs (graph), 
	FOREIGN KEY(branch) REFERENCES branches (branch)
)
create_graphs:
CREATE TABLE graphs (
	graph TEXT NOT NULL, 
	type TEXT NOT NULL, 
	PRIMARY KEY (graph), 
	CHECK (type IN ('Graph', 'DiGraph', 'MultiGraph', 'MultiDiGraph'))
)
create_node_val:
CREATE TABLE node_val (
	graph TEXT NOT NULL, 
	node TEXT NOT NULL, 
	"key" TEXT NOT NULL, 
	branch TEXT NOT NULL, 
	turn INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	tick INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	prev TEXT, 
	value TEXT, 
	PRIMARY KEY (graph, node, "key", branch, turn, tick), 
	FOREIGN KEY(graph, node) REFERENCES nodes (graph, node), 
	FOREIGN KEY(branch) REFERENCES branches (branch)
)
create_nodes:
CREATE TABLE nodes (
	graph TEXT NOT NULL, 
	node TEXT NOT NULL, 
	branch TEXT NOT NULL, 
	turn INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	tick INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	extant BOOLEAN NOT NULL, 
	PRIMARY KEY (graph, node, branch, turn, tick), 
	FOREIGN KEY(graph) REFERENCES graphs (graph), 
	FOREIGN KEY(branch) REFERENCES branches (branch), 
	CHECK (extant IN (0, 1))
)
create_turns:
CREATE TABLE turns (
	branch TEXT NOT NULL, 
	turn INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	end_tick INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	plan_end_tick INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	PRIMARY KEY (branch, turn)
)
del_edge_val_after: DELETE FROM edge_val WHERE edge_val.graph = ? AND edge_val.orig = ? AND edge_val.dest = ? AND edge_val.idx = ? AND edge_val."key" = ? AND edge_val.branch = ? AND (edge_val.turn > ? OR edge_val.turn = ? AND edge_val.tick >= ?)
del_edges_after: DELETE FROM edges WHERE edges.graph = ? AND edges.orig = ? AND edges.dest = ? AND edges.idx = ? AND edges.branch = ? AND (edges.turn > ? OR edges.turn = ? AND edges.tick >= ?)
del_graph_val_after: DELETE FROM graph_val WHERE graph_val.graph = ? AND graph_val."key" = ? AND graph_val.branch = ? AND (graph_val.turn > ? OR graph_val.turn = ? AND graph_val.tick >= ?)
del_node_val_after: DELETE FROM node_val WHERE node_val.graph = ? AND node_val.node = ? AND node_val."key" = ? AND node_val.branch = ? AND (node_val.turn > ? OR node_val.turn = ? AND node_val.tick >= ?)
del_nodes_after: DELETE FROM nodes WHERE nodes.graph = ? AND nodes.node = ? AND nodes.branch = ? AND (nodes.turn > ? OR nodes.turn = ? AND nodes.tick >= ?)

SELECT edge_val.graph, edge_val.orig, edge_val.dest, edge_val.idx, edge_val."key", edge_val.branch, edge_val.turn, edge_val.tick, edge_val.prev, edge_val.value 
FROM edge_val ORDER BY edge_val.graph, edge_val.orig, edge_val.dest, edge_val.idx, edge_val."key", edge_val.branch, edge_val.turn, edge_val.tick
edge_val_get_branch:
SELECT edge_val.graph, edge_val.orig, edge_val.dest, edge_val.idx, edge_val."key", edge_val.turn, edge_val.tick, edge_val.prev, edge_val.value 
FROM edge_val 
WHERE edge_val.branch = ? ORDER BY edge_val.turn, edge_val.tick
edge_val_get_branch_until:
SELECT edge_val.graph, edge_val.orig, edge_val.dest, edge_val.idx, edge_val."key", edge_val.turn, edge_val.tick, edge_val.prev, edge_val.value 
FROM edge_val 
WHERE edge_val.branch = ? AND (edge_val.turn < ? OR edge_val.turn = ? AND edge_val.tick <= ?) ORDER BY edge_val.turn, edge_val.tick
edge_val_get_branch_window:
SELECT edge_val.graph, edge_val.orig, edge_val.dest, edge_val.idx, edge_val."key", edge_val.turn, edge_val.tick, edge_val.prev, edge_val.value 
FROM edge_val 
WHERE edge_val.branch = ? AND (edge_val.turn > ? OR edge_val.turn = ? AND edge_val.tick >= ?) AND (edge_val.turn < ? OR edge_val.turn = ? AND edge_val.tick <= ?) ORDER BY edge_val.turn, edge_val.tick
